summary: 该插件用于检测PbootCMS系统是否存在CVE-2018-16356 SQL注入漏洞，通过发送特定payload并验证响应内容来确认漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the PbootCMS system has the CVE-2018-16356 SQL injection vulnerability. It confirms the existence of the vulnerability by sending a specific payload and verifying the response content.
